headline: The Surprising Stock Investors Should Stop Buying Despite a Likely Stock Split
summary: The idea of not buying Home Depot (NYSE: HD) may seem to make little sense.  Few stocks have matched its track record for overall returns (total return of 421% over the past decade compared to the S&P 500's 250% return).  There appears to be some pressure for a stock split for Home Depot.
